page.title: 07Why people move to Dalston
page.content: We have done a survey to find out how many people moved out of all of the juniors in our school There were 37 juniors in our school that moved to Dalston and there are 92 juniors in the whole of our school . The main reason why they moved was because of their father's job and there were 16 giving that reason altogether The second reason was because they wanted bigger houses, 4 people moved to Dalston because they wanted better houses, 3 people moved because they liked the school and 2 people moved because of family health, 1 person wanted to move because of their mum's job and 1 person moved because they wanted to be near some friends.
